{"id":"barachias-berechiah","term":"Barachias, Berechiah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>4 (q.v.), whom Jehovah hath blessed, father of the prophet Zechariah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Zechariah 1:1\">Zech. 1:1</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Zechariah 1:7\">7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Matthew 23:35\">Matt. 23:35</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Zechariah 1:1","Zechariah 1:7","Matthew 23:35"]}